The specials are good deals and they have them everyday, as well as one available any day of the week. They're really quick about the food and service. The chicken n fish combo is my favorite, but their burgers are also amazing and pretty big compared to other places. They do have free refills on drinks, so that's a major plus. The only downside is that if you order a dish that gets you a sauce, you only get 2 packets, you'd have to pay for an extras, but it's a small price to pay as the sauce adds to the experience of the food.
